title: SLOW DOWN, Our Diana? 6.18.20

description:
In episode 654, Miles and guest host Scam Goddess Laci Mosley are joined by comedian Zahra Noorbakhsh to discuss the lack of transparency around the PPP fund, how to fix our economy, Kristen Stewart being cast as Princess Diana, and more!

FOOTNOTES:

  1. The $500 billion black box
  2. COVID-19 Broke the Economy. What If We Don’t Fix It?
  3. Pablo Larraín To Direct Kristen Stewart As Princess Diana In ‘Spencer’, On When Lady Di Rejected The Fairy Tale Ending: Virtual Cannes Hot Package
  4. WATCH: Tom Misch x Yussef Dayes - Kyiv
